data.description: PRICE REDUCED! BEAUTIFUL HOME BUILT IN 2019 WITH TONS OF UPGRADES LOCATED ON CUL-DE-SAC STREET! This home features an open floor plan that combines the kitchen, dining space, and living room making it perfect for spending quality time with friends and family! This is the Orchid II floor plan by LGI homes! This kitchen boasts wood cabinets with ample cabinet space and breakfast bar that overlooks the living room! The spacious Master Bed/Bathroom has a walk-in closet and beautiful bathroom! Some other great features of this home include its inside laundry closet, tile floors througout main area, and 1 year old 16'x10' shed out back that was professionally permited and installed! All of this in the family friendly community of Hill N Dale which is conveniently located close to parks, schools, shopping, dining, and just minutes from I-75 and SR 50! There are no HOA or CDD fees! Bring your boat, jetski, or RV and park it in your driveway! Set up your showing, this one will go fast!
